header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Duke's Wendell Carter Jr. tries to score in the paint, but Bonzie Colson has other ideas, rejecting Carter's shot and securing the board.
videos.headline: ND's Colson stuffs Duke's Carter at the rim

videos.description: Duke's Grayson Allen throws a lob from just inside half court to Marvin Bagley III who easily throws it down to complete the alley-oop.
videos.headline: Allen tosses lob for Bagley slam

videos.description: Grayson Allen scores nine straight points for Duke, knocking down three consecutive triples to extend the Blue Devils' first-half lead.
videos.headline: Allen catches fire from deep

videos.description: With time winding down in the first half, Fighting Irish forward John Mooney rises up for a two-handed slam just before the halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Notre Dame closes 1st half in style

videos.description: Notre Dame head coach Mike Brey calls Duke's offense "explosive" and says the Fighting Irish will need to light up the scoreboard to come away with a victory.
videos.headline: Brey: ND will 'have to score 90' points to win

videos.description: Duke inbounds the ball to Wendell Carter Jr. who goes up for a slam, but Notre Dame's Martinas Geben emphatically swats his shot away.
videos.headline: ND's Geben protects the rim

videos.description: Duke guard Trevon Duval picks off a pass and finishes in transition with a one-handed flush to give the Blue Devils a double-digit lead.
videos.headline: Duval steals and slams

videos.description: Duke's Marvin Bagley III is dominant in his postseason debut, scoring from all over the floor to give the Blue Devils a commanding lead.
videos.headline: Bagley does it all against Notre Dame

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell pushes the ball ahead to TJ Gibbs Jr. who breaks out a sweet Eurostep to get the hoop and the harm.
videos.headline: ND's Gibbs Eurosteps into and-1 bucket

videos.description: As the lone senior on Duke's roster, Grayson Allen says he prepared his teammates for the postseason by stressing the importance of elimination games.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Allen takes leadership role for Duke) 2018/03/08

videos.headline: Allen takes leadership role for Duke
